         <abstract id="aspace_48edc37b03fd91de1461fde54e6fd0c1">Seventy-two letters from Jaime Arando to his father, Francisco Arando, dating from 1937-1940. Jaime Arando was active on the Ebro Front, spent time in a concentration camp, and later joined the National Army.</abstract>
