      <scopecontent id="aspace_41888fc1401ece69be7eb6992f4aa976">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Seventy-two letters from Jaime Arando to his father, Francisco Arando, dating from 1937-1940. Jaime Arando was active on the Ebro Front, spent time in a concentration camp, and later joined the National Army.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
